item.title: You Won't Believe What Happened When This Person Tried To Build The World's Largest Paper Airplane!
item.description: Introduction Have you ever wanted to build something that’s never been done before? Well, one person did just that, and the result was amazing! Read on to find out what happened when this person tried to build the world’s largest paper airplane. Background of the Person’s Attempt The person in question was an engineer from the United States. He had a passion for paper airplanes and was determined to build the world’s largest one.
